    "description": "RML Hospital Holdings Services, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Senior Doctor for our Raipur operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout RML Hospital Holdings Services:\nRML Hospital Holdings Services is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Maintain sterile environments and follow infection control protocols\n• Attend continuing medical education programs and training\n• Ensure patient privacy and maintain confidentiality\n• Administer medications and treatments as prescribed\n• Participate in quality improvement initiatives and clinical audits\n• Maintain accurate clinical documentation in electronic health records\n• Coordinate with multidisciplinary teams for comprehensive patient management\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Master's degree preferred\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Clinical Research\n• Proficiency in Clinical Documentation\n• Proficiency in Medical Coding\n• Proficiency in Health Informatics\n• Proficiency in Diagnostic Skills\n• Proficiency in Pharmacovigilance\n• Proficiency in Patient Care\n• Proficiency in Surgical Procedures\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Learning & development budget\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Raipur, Chhattisgarh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with RML Hospital Holdings Services!",
